==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quinoxaline
<hw>Quin*ox"a*line</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Quin</ets>oline + gly<ets>oxal</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Any one of a series of complex nitrogenous bases
obtained by the union of certain aniline derivatives with glyoxal or
with certain ketones.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>chinoxaline</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

